collection.name: Rubrics
collection.description:
API Calls for the D2L Hypermedia rubrics APIs

Note that the calls in this documentation use a url (for example localhost:44444). You can alternatively specify this using tenant ids in the following format

```
https://{{tenant id}}.rubrics.api.dev.brightspace.com
```

this would replace:

```
http://{{url}}/d2l/api/hm/rubrics
```

in the examples shown in this documentation

detail.name: OK
detail.detail: Standard response for successful HTTP requests. The actual response will depend on the request method used. In a GET request, the response will contain an entity corresponding to the requested resource. In a POST request the response will contain an entity describing or containing the result of the action.
